persona-component triad — the Pi harness adapted for the persona system. Lives as its own component-tree (daemon + signal-persona-pi working contract + owner-signal-persona-pi policy contract + thin pi CLI client). Runs inside a terminal-cell (the persona-terminal-shaped surface that handles Unix-side I/O), but is NOT confined to it: Persona Pi can also talk directly to the harness API. The terminal-cell is the Unix-interaction conduit; the harness-API path is the more accessible logic surface, used because Pi is extensively customizable and exposes far more than terminal I/O.|] Zero Minimum Zero [])) (1q5w ([(Technology (Software (Intelligence AgentSystems)))] Decision [|The recording system's intent-capture stage (currently sketched in /145 §6) is a per-call runtime LLM function, not an agent. It receives speech-to-text output, extracts intent for logging, may rephrase to clean STT typos / structure thoughts better, and may route sections of the prompt to different long-lived agents based on topic. The function has no persistent identity; it's invoked per audio span. Long-lived agents (the ones with cryptographic identity per intent 120) consume the routed prompt sections; the intent-capture itself stays stateless. This refines /145's design — the extractor was described neutrally as 'the model'; the function-vs-agent distinction makes the call's shape explicit and unlocks the per-call context provisioning pattern.|] Zero Minimum Zero [])) (1rci ([(Technology (Software (Data Formats)))] Clarification [NOTA braces are the native structural key-value map delimiter. Schema reads a brace object as key-value structure, not as a schema macro form. Key-value-ness belongs to the low-level NOTA structure; macros may consume these structures at schema positions.] Zero Minimum Zero [])) (1rqy ([(Information Documentation) (Technology (Software (Engineering Architecture)))] Correction [The criome psyche-facing approval component is named mentci - the existing mentci-egui and 