)] Decision [Confirmed: designers recreate their feature branch worktrees under ~/wt/github.com/LiGoldragon/<repo>/<feature-name>/ and rebase as living feature branches; operators rebase those branches onto main. The /tmp prototype worktrees retire after relocation.] Zero Minimum Zero [])) (ov30 ([(Technology (Software (Engineering Architecture)))] Principle [A struct field's role is its type, so no struct has two fields of the same type. Distinct roles are distinct types, giving dimensional correctness: Height and Width are both metres yet cannot be interchanged or multiplied as like. Repetition is a keyed collection, never repeated fields, since a Vector is a Map over an ordinal index. Field-name equals type-name is the default, and an explicit field name signals a missing type or a collection. Full type-level enforcement is aspirational. The principle guides schema and nota design now.] Zero Minimum Zero [schema nota])) (ox2x ([(Technology (Software (Programming Macros)))] Clarification [Macro-schema builtin variants are data-carrying at node definition points] Zero Minimum Zero [])) (ox7e ([(Technology (Software (Data Persistence)))] Principle [When schema-derived components expose a reusable storage need, do not merely port them to a mismatched current sema-engine API; improve the shared engine surface so generated SEMA code expresses its real storage identity and query needs directly.] Zero Minimum Zero [])) (oxur ([(Technology (Software (Distributed ProtocolDesign)))] Decision [|Every message prefixed with the 64-bit Tier 1 micro type marker; receivers know type + size + structure of the root object from the prefix; rkyv zero-copy compat (read directly from memory after network-fingerprint check); tap-anywhere sync emission default-on with build-time disable for faster execution; the prefix-of-every-message pattern doubles as observation channel|] Zero Minimum Zero [])) (oxy1 ([(Technology (Software (Data Modeling)))] Decision [|Settled: the removal-candidate